"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9tA","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/12-rakaat-al-sunan-al-rawatib\/","url_meta":{"origin":36430,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Twelve raka\u2019at of al-Sunan al-Rawatib prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever perseveres in performing twelve cycles of prayer from the Sunnah, Allah will build a house for him in Paradise. They are four cycles before noon prayer and two after it, two cycles after sunset prayer, two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-between-maghrib-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":36430,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Continuous praying between Maghrib and Isha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: I came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I performed the evening prayer with him. The Prophet continued to pray until the evening prayer. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3781 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17429,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/prophet-sleeps-after-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":36430,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Isha: The Prophet sleeps after evening prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not sleep before evening prayer\u00a0and he would not stay up after it. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 702 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28121,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/ten-rakaat-sunan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36430,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary Sunan prayers throughout day","auth